    "actor": "https://uofa.net/synth/actor/morrison-credibility-lead",
    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "Under the Minimal profile, the structured Context of Use link is not required and the assessment is recorded as accepted for archival purposes. The intended use scope — regulatory submission supporting a Class III implantable VAD for adults with end-stage heart failure operating at 2000–3500 RPM and 3–6 L/min — is described in the Claim prose at https://uofa.net/synth/claim/vad-hemolysis-cfd-prediction-claim and in the Requirement at https://uofa.net/synth/req/vad-hemolysis-mrl5-requirement. Reviewers should note that all 13 credibility factors show achieved levels below required levels; the Accepted outcome reflects only procedural completeness of the Minimal profile submission, not substantive credibility sufficiency for regulatory use.",
